{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/spiswa-about-616x150.png?t=1738278181\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/03-howdidtheygethere__1_.gif?t=1738278181\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Samar is a young witch who works the spirit-swapping night shift in the eastern outskirts of Demashq. A recent spike in spirits crossing over from another dimension within the borders of the city has them puzzling over what\u2019s going on.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With friends needing help - and a popular band scheduled to kick off their big comeback tour in Demashq - Samar needs to work quickly before the city is overrun with stans and spirits alike!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/05-yallaHabibi.gif?t=1738278181\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Spirit Swap: Lofi Beats to Match-3 To blends two major sources of inspiration: the joyful, colorful puzzle mechanics of Panel de Pon and the heartfelt and playful storytelling of visual novels/dating sims.</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/spiswa-features-616x150.png?t=1738278181\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Swap to a custom lofi soundtrack</strong> by the incredible Meltycanon.\u00a0 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cast powerful spells</strong> by arranging spirits into special patterns to unlock potent powers.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Bond with a diverse cast of witches and demons</strong>\u2026 and maybe even smooch.\u00a0\u00a0 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Decorate your bedroom.</strong> Earn trinkets and keepsakes as you play, then place them to decorate Samar\u2019s room.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Enjoy unique game modes</strong>, including Endless and local Versus!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/04-kanonMatch__1_.gif?t=1738278181\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738278181","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/page.bg.jpg?t=1738278181","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/781b59084efdcd11133ee90e7b3d003164442fca/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738278181","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/781b59084efdcd11133ee90e7b3d003164442fca/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738278181","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":1759570,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1592170/extras/spiswa-about-616x150.png?t=1738278181\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steams